---
// About bileşeni
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-dark-light/30">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary mb-6">
          Kasım Aksoy <span class="text-primary">Hukuk & Danışmanlık</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-secondary/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          15 yıllık deneyimimizle, müvekkillerimize en yüksek kalitede hukuki hizmet sunuyoruz. 
          Güven, şeffaflık ve başarı odaklı yaklaşımımızla hukuki sorunlarınıza çözüm üretiyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <!-- Left Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-6">
            Neden Bizi Seçmelisiniz?
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">15 Yıllık Deneyim</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary/70">Uzun yıllara dayanan tecrübemizle, karmaşık hukuki sorunları çözüme kavuşturuyoruz.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Güvenilirlik</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary/70">Müvekkil gizliliği ve güvenilirlik ilkelerimizden asla taviz vermiyoruz.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Hızlı Çözüm</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary/70">Zamanında ve etkili çözümlerle hukuki süreçlerinizi hızlandırıyoruz.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Content - Image/Logo -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary-light/20 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-primary/30">
            <img src="/logo.jpeg" alt="Kasım Aksoy Hukuk & Danışmanlık" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl">
            <div class="mt-6 text-center">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Kasım Aksoy</h4>
              <p class="text-primary font-medium">Kurucu Ortak</p>
              <p class="text-secondary/70 text-sm mt-2">T.C. NO: 284 114 47 832</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Statistics -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">500+</div>
          <p class="text-secondary font-semibold">Başarılı Dava</p>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 text-sm mt-2">15 yılda tamamlanan dava sayısı</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">98%</div>
          <p class="text-secondary font-semibold">Müvekkil Memnuniyeti</p>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 text-sm mt-2">Referanslarımızın memnuniyet oranı</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center bg-dark-light/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-8 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">15</div>
          <p class="text-secondary font-semibold">Yıllık Deneyim</p>
          <p class="text-secondary/70 text-sm mt-2">Hukuk alanında uzmanlık süresi</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary mb-8">Değerlerimiz</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-dark-light/30 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Güven</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary/70">Müvekkillerimizin güvenini kazanmak ve korumak en büyük önceliğimizdir.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-light/30 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Deneyim</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary/70">Uzun yıllara dayanan tecrübemizle en iyi hukuki çözümleri sunuyoruz.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-dark-light/30 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Başarı</h4>
            <p class="text-secondary/70">Müvekkillerimizin başarısı için çalışır, sonuç odaklı yaklaşım sergileriz.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 